snippet.title: Dino Frontier - PlayStation Experience 2016: Announcement Trailer | PSVR
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/dino-frontier-ps4/

 Frontier lets you build and manage a frontier settlement in a world where the wild west and Jurassic collide.

You assume the role of Big Mayor overlooking your settlement in tabletop scale VR. You must carefully balance resources while growing your town. Wild dinosaurs roam the land acting as both dangerous foe and tantalizing asset.

http://www.dinofrontier.com

© 2016 Uber Entertainment
